      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures, version control, and regression test suites. Software quality assurance documentation reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
