    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device submissions; the overall evidence package supports an Accepted decision.",
